Class ListSpanStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.gui.dock.station.support.ListSpanStrategy
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlapSpanStrategy

    public abstract class ListSpanStrategy
extends Object
    Manages the Spans of a DockStation that orders its Dockables like a list.
